title: big.brother.uk.s15e03.of.10.live.from.the.house.the.live.surpris
description:
Watch this after Big Brother UK S15E05


Despite the housemates only having been in the compound for a few days, Big Brother shakes things up by introducing a twist to proceedings. Yesterday was the first nominations, with Power Housemate Pauline given a `killer nomination' - one housemate who will face possible eviction every week from now onwards. Could it be the announcement of that? Or does Big Brother have something else up his sleeve?
